sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Pi
    participant Extension
    participant Disk as ~/.pi/agent/memory/
    participant DB as sessions.db

    Note over Pi,Disk: ── Session Start ──
    Pi->>Extension: session_start event
    Extension->>Disk: loadFromDisk() — MEMORY.md + USER.md + failures.md + skills/
    Extension-->>Extension: Capture frozen snapshot (memory + failures + skill index)

    Note over Pi,Disk: ── System Prompt Injection ──
    Pi->>Extension: before_agent_start event
    Extension-->>Pi: systemPrompt + frozen memory + failures block + skill index

    Note over Pi,DB: ── Session Search + Capture ──
    User->>Pi: work normally
    Pi->>Extension: memory / skill / session_search tools as needed
    Extension->>Disk: atomic writes for memory + skills
    Extension->>DB: extended memory + indexed sessions available on demand

    Note over Pi,DB: ── Candidate Extraction Pipeline (v0.7) ──
    Pi->>Extension: /memory-index-sessions (bulk) or session auto-index on shutdown
    Extension->>DB: store sessions/messages in SQLite
    User->>Pi: /memory-candidates-shadow-run
    Extension-->>Pi: read-only quality report
    User->>Pi: /memory-candidates-rebuild
    Extension->>DB: rebuild candidate projection from indexed SQLite session messages

    Note over Pi,DB: ── Candidate Review + Promotion ──
    User->>Pi: /memory-review-candidates
    Extension-->>Pi: TUI review queue with approve/reject/edit/merge
    User->>Pi: promote approved candidates
    Extension->>Pi: confirm skill creation
    Extension->>Disk: save skill draft to skills/
    Extension->>DB: mark candidates promoted

    Note over Pi,Disk: ── Background Learning ──
    Pi->>Extension: turn_end (10 turns or 15 tool calls)
    Extension->>Pi: pi.exec("pi -p", reviewPrompt)
    Note right of Pi: Saves memories/failures

    Note over Pi,Disk: ── Auto-Skill Nudge (existing path) ──
    Pi->>Extension: complex task threshold met
    Extension->>Pi: pi.exec("pi -p", skillExtractionPrompt)
    Note right of Pi: Auto-skill prompt path still exists<br/>alongside reviewed candidate promotion

    Note over Pi,Disk: ── Session End ──
    Pi->>Extension: session_shutdown event
    Extension->>Pi: pi.exec("pi -p", flushPrompt)
    Extension->>DB: auto-index latest session for future search/extraction
